productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Bhutan and I bought one.
My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 6 yard and weights 12 pound.
My chicken loves to play with it.
